attribs.name: character_backstory
attribs.current:
full name :blue moon

blue is a merchent girl thats family was elivated to noble hood in the town sigle. blues child hood freind was adopted by the leader of sigle and was trained to beacome the next leader of sigle. blues mother had almost died when the peapole of sigle were liberated from the preveus empress of sigle. as blue grew older she started to feel that dragor should be more than a freind. the day blue was going to confess her love to dragor he left on a "quest" witch she later found out was a quest to prove himself to blue from his adopted father. blue took a horse, some money, and some equipment and set of to find dragor. she arives at the tavern after her horse died and she walked a week without food or water trying to find him. her story starts when she colapses in the guild tavern unknowing she had stumbled apon her loves new home.
